io.jenetics.xml

Class Writers.DoubleChromosome

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.jenetics.xml.Writers.DoubleChromosome
  • Enclosing class:
    Writers

    public static final class Writers.DoubleChromosome
extends Object
    This class contains static writer methods for DoubleChromosome objects.

    Writer code

    final DoubleChromosome value = DoubleChromosome.of(0.0, 1.0, 3); try (AutoCloseableXMLStreamWriter xml = XML.writer(System.out, " ")) { Writers.DoubleChromosome.writer().write(value, xml); }
    XML output 
     
 <double-chromosome length="3">
     <min>0.0</min>
     <max>1.0</max>
     <alleles>
         <allele>0.27251556008507416</allele>
         <allele>0.003140816229067145</allele>
         <allele>0.43947528327497376</allele>
     </alleles>
 </double-chromosome>
